          <span className="mx-4">◆ Gray&apos;s Anatomy listed ₹1250 Afzalgunj</span>
          <span className="mx-4">◆ Laxmikant order placed LB Nagar</span>
          <span className="mx-4">◆ HC Verma Part 1+2 sold SR Nagar</span>
